                    <h1 style="text-align:center;color:#bcce98;font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode';  color:#808080;">Hostel Rules</h1>
                    <p>
                        1.This is your second home and be at home as a member of MACFAST family.<br />
                        2.Please bring your parent/guardian at the time of admission.<br />
                        3.Ragging in any form is stictly prohibited.<br />
                        4.Please pay the fee for every 6 months in advance.Delay in payment will result in fine.<br />
                        5.Hostel accomadation is provided primarily for attending the classeson time.So<br />
                        inmates are not expected to remain in the hostel during class hours,without the written permission of the warden.<br />
                        6.Please avoid cutting classes and absenting without valid reasons.The reasons for absent,if any should be intimated to the warden<br />
                        in writing in advance.<br />
                        7.Please make necessary entries in the register,when inmates go out for various purposes.<br />
                        8.The gates of the hostel will closed at 7pm and,there after entry/exit is permitted only on prior permission from the warden.<br />
                        9.The inmates can use the college library from 8:30PM TO 9:45PM with special permission and they should turn up to the hostel before 10PM.<br />
                        10.Visitors are permitted only up to 6PM.However visitors are not to be taken to the rooms of inmates.<br />
                        11.Please don&#39;t take any food items to the room,either from the mess or from outside.<br />
                        12.Please wash and clean your rooms,toilets and wash basins regulaly and keep them clean and tidy.Personal hygiene should be maintained.(common areas will be cleaned by the cleaning staff).<br />
                        13.Please maintain discipline &amp; decorum,both inside &amp; outside the hostel.Unruly behaviour should be avoided and basic courtesy should be observed.<br />
                        Responsible behaviour is expected from all. 14.Please avoid shouting,howling,litering etc.<br />
                        15.Please don&#39;t cause any loss or damage to hostel properties.<br />
                        16.Please don&#39;t paste,nail or write anything on the walls or any other places.<br />
                        17.Please dress properly inside the hostel.<br />
                        18.Please don&#39;t spread washed cloths on the railings or window bars for drying.Kepp them at the areas provided for the same.<br />
                        19.Please swith off lights at 11PM,and maintain absolute silence therafter.<br />
                        20.Utmost economy should be observed in the use of power,water &amp; other utilities.<br />
                        21.Please don&#39;t sit on the compound walls of the hostel or adjacent compounds.<br />
                        22.Always remember that maintaining good relationship with others is the secret of happiness.<br />
                        23.Please hand over the keys to the caretaker when you go home or when you vacate the hostel.<br />
                        24.Please clear the dues and hand over the keys to the caretaker whe you vacate the hostel.<br />
                        25.Please keep your personal properties securely and management will not be responsible for any loss of properties.<br />
                        26.All facilites available in the hostel are for the use of inmates; for BONAFIDE use.<br />
                        27.The above rules are indicative and not exhansive.<br />
